Thousand_Oaks.Westlake Golf Course: Westlake Golf Course is an 18-hole regulation length golf course located in Westlake Village, California, USA. It is an 18-hole course designed by Ted Robinson, ASGCA in 1964. It features 5,080 yards (4,650 m) of golf from the longest tees for a par of 67. The course rating is 63.2 and it has a slope rating of 93.
